txt.en: The Orcs have established tents and barricades to cut off the passage of Mudmul-charâf.\n\nYou should destroy the dwellings and defences of the Orcs to clear the passage in favour of the dwarves' expedition.
You have destroyed the dwellings and defences of the enemy in Mudmul-charâf.\n\nThe dwarves passing to and from the Twenty-first Hall will be in your debt for this good deed.
The Orcs have established tents and barricades to cut off the passage of Mudmul-charâf.
Orc tents and barricades can be found in Mudmul-charâf, a passage in north-western Zelem-melek.\n\nYou should destroy the makeshift dwellings and defences of the Orcs.
You have destroyed the dwellings and defences of the enemy in Mudmul-charâf.
